DESCRIPTION: Tadbart n uḍfaṛ n uwiki i yisenfaṛen Wikimedia.
LASTREVONLY: Sken kan asnifel aneggaru s usebter
FLAGS: Sken anayen deg umḍiq n yismawen n tutlayt
LOGEVENT_DELETE_REVISION: <user> yesnifel iẓri n uceggir ɣef usebter <page>
LOGEVENT_PROTECT_MODIFY: <user> ibeddel ammesten ɣef usebter <page> s iɣewwaṛen {{protection_level}}
LOGEVENT_PROTECT_MOVE: <user> yewwi iɣewwaṛen n ummesten n <page> ar <page title={{target_title}}>
LOGEVENT_MOVE: <user> ibeddel isem n usebter <page> s <page title={{target_title}}>
LOGEVENT_BLOCK_BLOCK: <user> isewḥel <user name={{title}}> s tengazt n tagara n {{duration}} akked iɣewwaṛen {{flags|list}}
LOGEVENT_BLOCK_REBLOCK: <user> isnifel iɣewwaṛen n usewḥel n <user name={{title}}> s tenzagt n tagara n {{duration}} akked iɣewwaren {{flags|list}}
LOGEVENT_RIGHTS_AUTOPROMOTE: <user> yessuli s wudem awurman aswir n {{oldgroups|list}} ar {{newgroups|list}}
LOGEVENT_RIGHTS_RIGHTS: <user> ibeddel attekki ar ugraw i <user name={{title}}>, si {{oldgroups|list}} ar {{newgroups|list}}
LOGEVENT_NEWUSERS_BYEMAIL: Amiḍan n useqdac <user name={{title}}> yerna-t <user> sakin awal uffir yettwazen s yimayl
LOGEVENT_RENAMEUSER: <user> yesnifel isem n useqdac <user name={{olduser}}> ({{edits}} tiẓrigin) ar <user name={{newuser}}>
LOGEVENT_TRANSLATION_ASSOCIATE: <user> YErna asebter izemren ad ittwasuqel <page> ar ugraw yedduklen {{aggregategroup}}
LOGEVENT_TRANSLATION_DISSOCIATE: <user> yekkes asebter izemren ad yettwasuqel <page> seg ugraw yedduklen {{aggregategroup}}
OAUTH_FAILURE_TITLE: Asesteb s OAuth ur yeddi ara
OAUTH_FAILURE_CONTENT: Asesteb ur yeddi ara, ahat tekkseḍ tasiregt i usnas-agi. Ma ulac aɣilif, ffeɣ sakin qqen. Talɣut n tuccḍa: {{error}}
SERVER_ERROR_CONTENT: Ulac tabdart n uḍfaṛ yettwafen. Wagi d tuccḍa tagensant n uqeddac., ldi aneqqis n tidyanin ma yella ugur yezga.
API_ERROR_CONTENT: Tuttra n API ur teddi ara, tangalt n tuccḍa d {{errorcode}} , talɣut : {{errorinfo}}
ONELINE: Tarusi n usebter tamensayt n tebdart n uḍfaṛ
HIDEOWNEDITS: Ffer tiẓrigin-iw n tebdart n uḍfaṛ
UNDO: Asefsex asnifel-agi, ad d-yeldi iccer amaynut s teskant
WATCHLIST_REMOVE: Kkes asebter-agi seg tebdart n uḍfaṛ
WATCHLIST_ADD: Rnu asebter-agi ar tebdart n uḍfaṛ
ORES_OPTION: Sken amgired n usefsex yettwasnen s ORES
ORES_TOOLTIP: Sken s wudem awurman amgired n usefsex yettwassnen, wali  [[:meta:ORES]] ɣef ugar n telqayt.
FLAGGEDREVS_OPTION: Sken amgired n teẓrigin yettṛaǧun taɣuri
FLAGGEDREVS_TOOLTIP: Sken amgiren n ibeddilen ur yettwaɣran ara, ma ɣur-k azref n tulsa n tɣuri i uwiki iseqdacen asiɣzef FlaggedRevs.
